{"tid":1027206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"肺癌爸爸瘦骨嶙峋 為1歲女要打勝仗","createTime":"2019-02-18T16:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T04:49:28.000Z","uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed361cabaff1c7a4df51e2abbe834c04a911abb1","tid":1027206,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:07:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190218/59269567\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190218%2F59269567&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEmLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=17ef1179\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190218%2F59269567&h=d5d3b7d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190218/59269567</a><br />\n<br />\n42歲的振哥，於一年半前當上爸爸，當時女兒剛出生，滿以為好日子降臨，卻因背痛不適求醫揭發患上肺癌。噩耗傳來，他及妻子頓時陷於徬徨，妻子忙着照顧初生女兒，亦要分身兼顧照料他。振哥眼見高齡母親常常為他奔波，陷於人生交叉點的他決定展開治療，要為初生女兒及母親重拾健康。剛過去的農曆新年他在醫院孤單度過，日前醫院以床位不足安排他出院，現時他正籌措藥費購買自費藥延續抗癌療程。<br />\n<br />\n記者：麥超億<br />\n<br />\n受肺癌折磨，振哥現時體重僅餘100磅，瘦至皮包骨，但腹部及雙腳嚴重腫脹，精神萎靡。採訪當日，醫護人員以醫院床位不足安排他出院，其81歲母親接報趕至醫院接他出院。當時一直卧病休息的振哥全身乏力，要由母親攙扶才能下床，之後乘車返回屯門大興邨寓所。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190218/large/1550462970_cb89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190218%2Flarge%2F1550462970_cb89.jpg&h=a5c713e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本好英俊.....而家變左骷髏骨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b877749fa5f8dc1f4ca0783c9e07e7efe03f1ea7","tid":1027206,"uid":154255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:35:28.000Z","msg":"無事之前 <br />\n成個超人咁<br />\n所以話健康幾重要"},{"pid":"29e4f82a2a19543562e45206d913e8ab5e1be26b","tid":1027206,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T16:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65aa3b90ddabc97ddf77637b6eced0621938ce1","tid":1027206,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:14:23.000Z","msg":"任職飲食業"},{"pid":"45883eb79b0f7fca527390bf48d84248c60198b4","tid":1027206,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"醫護人員以醫院床位不足安排他出院<br />\n<br />\n香港已完"}]}